snippet.title: 『Shurado』 - iOS / Android - 2nd PV
snippet.description:
["Shurado" official website]
http://ganbarion.com/shurado/

A hell where men who killed a lot of people fall into: "Shurado".
It is a strategic duel action game which you will control a man who fell into "Shurado" and aims at top while defeating enemies and collecting stronger weapon.


[Platform]
App Store
-iPhone 6s or later recommended.

Google Play(TM)
-Android OS 7.0 or later recommended.
-Snapdragon 820 or later recommended.

*There are some machines incompatible.



©2017 GANBARION Co., Ltd.
